    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:2",
      "text": "Created & Written by（创建与撰写者）",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:3",
      "text": "：Christopher Herrick",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:4",
      "text": "Curated and Edited（策划与编辑）：",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:5",
      "text": "Leif Pedersen",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:6",
      "text": "Elucidae 是 CG Supervisor（CG 监督/主管）“",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:7",
      "text": "Christopher Herrick",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:9",
      "text": "RenderMan for Solaris 项目由 Pixar 的",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:10",
      "text": "Leif Pedersen",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:12",
      "text": "这个 Solaris 项目是熟悉面向 openUSD 的 RenderMan-centric workflows 的绝佳方式，包括 mesh edits、geo settings、animations、materials、lights，以及使用 RenderMan 机器学习 Denoiser 的理想渲染设置。",
      "ascii_letters": 101,
      "cjk_chars": 32
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:14",
      "text": "该项目为艺术家提供了友好的交互方式，包括用于选择 animations 的下拉菜单，以及 Micropolygon Length 等有用的 geometry settings，便于调节 displacement 细节。",
      "ascii_letters": 56,
      "cjk_chars": 40
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:15",
      "text": "一个 look-dev node 展示了面向 Solaris 的 UX building 工作流，并提供对 grayscale wireframe material 的控制，从而可以轻松测试几何属性。",
      "ascii_letters": 54,
      "cjk_chars": 30
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:16",
      "text": "分层的 skin、eye 和 cloth materials 展示了 subsurface scattering、multi-lobe specular 和 fuzz shaders，并配有富有洞察力的 RenderMan pattern networks，可帮助你理解 Pixar 推荐的角色 look development 工作流。",
      "ascii_letters": 113,
      "cjk_chars": 31
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:17",
      "text": "Elucidae 是用户拆解 RenderMan-centric project 的好机会。该项目旨在利用 Solaris 为 RenderMan XPU 提供的优秀 openUSD workflows。祝你玩得开心！",
      "ascii_letters": 66,
      "cjk_chars": 28
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:18",
      "text": "About the Artist（艺术家简介）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:19",
      "text": "Christopher Herrick 是一位 CG Supervisor 和 Artist，参与过以下作品：",
      "ascii_letters": 36,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:20",
      "text": "Godzilla X Kong",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:21",
      "text": "Rings of Power Season 2",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d12cdeeb85:23",
      "text": "Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
